ActLegislative Instruments Re-enactment Act
PrecisLEGISLATIVE INSTRUMENTS RE-ENACTMENT REGULATIONS, NO. 5 which re-enacts, or provides the re-enactment of, certain instruments of a legislative nature that were orginally enacted in only one official language in order to resolve any uncertainty with respect to their legal validity.
